    {
        "id": "codecs-overview",
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Splix supports most of the common subtitle formats that are used in productions. If a format is not supported, you can request it to be supported, or check if the format is already on the [roadmap](https://splix.org/#/docs/codecs#roadmap). View the list below for currently supported codecs."
    },
